rules: // example App name is "Car Service". Address has a street address, city, state, zip. User has a name, email, user type, date joined, home address. User types are driver, client. Date joined is a date field. Home address is an address. Order has date, client, driver, source address, destination address, pickup time, order status, cost. Date is a date field. Order statuses are new, picked up, dropped off, cancelled. Client is a user. Driver is a user. Source address is an address. Destination address is an address. Main page title is "Welcome to Car Service" Main page content is "A Customer is always a customer!"
